Localis is a Geographic Information System. Database is handled by MySQL,
and a PHP web interface displays a map generated on the fly by Mapscript from 
Mapserver.

Version 0.5 propose contributive feeding of the map, 

(yes, it's very short, more verbose stuff will come soon).

